2002-06-30  Jerome Zago <jerome.zago@insalien.org>

		Better FHS compliance: binaries now go into /usr/games, static
		data into /usr/share/games/enigma, and variable data into
		/var/games/enigma (thanks Joel Mayes <bluebird@optushome.com.au>
		for your patch). This fixes bug #282.

